        <abstract> 
<p>Upset to learn he has misrepresented CD’s doctrine on Pangenesis [in <hi rend="italic">Proc. R. Soc. Lond.</hi> 19 (1871): 393–410]. Hopes that CD’s letter to <hi rend="italic">Nature</hi> [3 (1871): 502–3; <hi rend="italic">Collected papers</hi> 2: 165–7] will clarify the doctrine and attract attention to it.</p> 
